{"tid":2398553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眾新聞 黑龍江寒冬停止供暖  民眾不滿衝擊政府  質疑涉官商勾結","createTime":"2021-02-07T11:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T12:12:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"587febb147d8df86c1c76bdf7996c9d772e72ab4","tid":2398553,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"#黑龍江 #上訪 #官商勾結<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n黑龍江寒冬停止供暖 <br />\n民眾不滿衝擊政府 <br />\n質疑涉官商勾結<br />\nFeb 5, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/84JjWNDGGe8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F84JjWNDGGe8&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=fa42b4e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/84JjWNDGGe8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.4K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n黑龍江綏化市今早（周五）爆發大規模民眾上訪，當地居民因供暖問題，集體衝擊政府大樓。當地民眾指，供暖廠每年冬天都會以鍋爐維修等名義，停止供暖數天：「這熱電廠是有條不紊地在壞，想壞就壞，想甚麼時候壞就甚麼時候壞。」他們指，這次集體上訪是由於「老百姓反映沒人管」，是長期積累的結果，又質疑背後涉及官商勾結。<br />\n<br />\n【全文閲讀】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Mun0cW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Mun0cW&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=c5971bba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Mun0cW</a>"},{"pid":"9f673b5027d996ee33fa159a246d31fba29b8e31","tid":2398553,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"你班畜牲有咩資格嘈"},{"pid":"d163633f85c4c1d88953afe9eb35aa60f9dc0bb2","tid":2398553,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41178cc1c9bd8c15a32f2d34d5fd8b72d3ff40b4","tid":2398553,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"班人又收左美國佬錢<img src=\"/assets/